embeds.title: Sunshine Supply Event
embeds.description: Sunshine Supply Event is a semi-annual event where Super Card packs have increased drop rate of Hunting Medals and legendary heroes.

fields.name: Sunshine Supply V
value<text>: • Increased legendary hero drop: unlimited openings
• Available legendary hero: Poseidon, Selene, Kraken, Aly, Dracula, Apollo, Harrison, Drake, Chione, Davison, Seondeok, Charon, Frejya, Odin
• Approximate hero shard probability: Rare: 5.5%; Epic: 6.6%; Lego: 2.2%
